CM_ BO_ 2149580800 "100 ms heartbeat. State (0=INIT,1=STANDBY,2=ACTIVE). MOBO never self-faults.";
CM_ BO_ 2149580801 "Full 32-bit error and warning bitmasks (pure telemetry).";
CM_ BO_ 2149580802 "CAN TX/RX counters (lower 16 bits).";
CM_ BO_ 2149580816 "Battery, 5V rail, brake-input voltage, and raw LV current ADC count.";
CM_ BO_ 2149580832 "LV and HC current with running peaks.";
CM_ BO_ 2149580848 "Safety inputs: raw, debounced, and latched (telemetry only).";
CM_ BO_ 2149580864 "Commanded vs actual relay state with per-channel FSM.";
CM_ BO_ 2149581296 "VCU relay command. Byte 0 bit 0 = enable; byte 1 bits 0..3 = relay mask. Only command source MOBO honors.";
CM_ BO_ 2149581303 "System reset; any frame on this ID triggers a reset and payload is ignored.";
CM_ BO_ 2149581304 "Runtime config write. Param_ID per CONFIG_PARAM_* in config_manager.h.";

